{"tid":1032044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗老怪招】注入年輕血液保青春？FDA籲勿亂試","createTime":"2019-02-22T05:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T01:19:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af5e502be4bd5244840d651ead61b0f28cd611c5","tid":1032044,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T05:48:03.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）坊間的抗老療法層出不窮，近來美國有診所力推青春血漿療程，聲稱有逆齡、改善記憶力，甚至是治療多種老人病症的神奇功效。不過美國食品及藥物管理局（FDA）表示，目前並無證據顯示注血療法有藥效，呼籲民眾不要嘗試。<br />\n這種療程要價數千美元，診所聲稱使用的是年輕人捐出的血漿，輸血後除了逆齡抗老，甚至可以治療失智症、柏金遜症、認知障礙症、心臟病和創傷後遺症（PTSD）等。<br />\nFDA對療程表示關注，認為診所聲稱注入年輕人血漿的療效，沒有充足和良好管控的實驗佐證。FDA局長戈特利布（Scott Gottlieb）周二表示：「簡單地輸血漿並非良性干預的治療方式，不應隨意採用。」<br />\nFDA判斷療程可以投入市場之前，會仔細審查研究數據，新療法必須經過大量研究，才能證明它們是否安全有效。戈特利布表示，輸入年輕血液的療程顯然未經過這類測試，其安全及有效性不獲FDA認可。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190222/large/1550809669_5220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190222%2Flarge%2F1550809669_5220.jpg&h=fa223fac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3165b44b875024d54bc62401847d8d7a8d0e0d3","tid":1032044,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母變返中世紀魔女浸少女血咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c59f403728995d5d2a5c2ba4600e841fe3e067","tid":1032044,"uid":69841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"信嗰啲係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個療法真係得嘅話發明嗰個應該晨早拎咗諾貝爾奬"},{"pid":"cf77a9645fbf2241fc27b353c40f6910df108c04","tid":1032044,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"on 9"},{"pid":"08296d4eec3b4d8958ed7a71f5c02bd355e30c88","tid":1032044,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35c59f403728995d5d2a5c2ba4600e841fe3e067","tid":1032044,"uid":69841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"信嗰啲係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個療法真係得嘅話發明嗰個應該晨早拎咗諾貝爾奬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef1678f0c1354bfe826380a1ead67ace55d57ba","tid":1032044,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35c59f403728995d5d2a5c2ba4600e841fe3e067","tid":1032044,"uid":69841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"信嗰啲係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個療法真係得嘅話發明嗰個應該晨早拎咗諾貝爾奬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"佢地想拎達爾文獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a46df6acabda45bb340e8109849c102207ac185","tid":1032044,"uid":193131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為咁樣中左血傳染的病就好睇"},{"pid":"4483f3b7287145bdda22b99700e25e2be1011bb3","tid":1032044,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:13:24.000Z","msg":"mad max<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7bdf2050cfe2114cfa904dd5c5194f0a19e0a3","tid":1032044,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:13:47.000Z","msg":"+x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48439a23b87b69c4b9c31a5d13de988c969189f3","tid":1032044,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:19:01.000Z","msg":"天理教趙無極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}